title: SonicWall: Memory Usage
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/sonicwall
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the memory usage of SonicWall firewalls in percent.

 The levels for the usage in percent can be configured via the rule
 "SonicWall Memory usage". Default levels are 80%/95%.

 The check uses the SONICWALL-FIREWALL-IP-STATISTICS-MIB.

discovery:
 One service is created per host.
